<!doctype html>
<html lang=it>
<head>
<meta charset=UTF-8>
<meta name=viewport content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<link rel=icon href=images/favicon_io/favicon.svg type=image/svg+xml sizes=any>
<link rel=icon href=images/favicon_io/favicon-32x32.png type=image/png sizes=32x32>
<link rel=icon href=images/favicon_io/favicon-16x16.png type=image/png sizes=16x16>
<link rel=apple-touch-icon href=images/favicon_io/apple-touch-icon.png sizes=180x180>
<link rel=apple-touch-icon href=images/favicon_io/apple-touch-icon-167x167.png sizes=167x167>
<link rel=apple-touch-icon href=images/favicon_io/apple-touch-icon-152x152.png sizes=152x152>
<link rel=mask-icon href=images/favicon_io/safari-pinned-tab.svg color=#000000>
<link rel=manifest href=images/favicon_io/site.webmanifest>
<link rel=icon href=images/favicon_io/favicon.ico>
<title><%= data.siteTitle %></title>
<link rel=stylesheet href=/css/style.css>
<link rel=preconnect href=https://fonts.googleapis.com>
<link rel=preconnect href=https://fonts.gstatic.com crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel=stylesheet>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Helvetica+Neue:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel=stylesheet>
</head>
<body>
<header>
<div class=container-img><img class=logo-img src=/images/favicon_io/android-chrome-512x512.png loading=lazy></div>
<div class=logo> <span class=logo-text>GIOVANNA EMANUELA PLOMITALLO</span></div>
<button class=menu-toggle id=menuToggle>☰</button>
<nav class=nav-menu id=navMenu>
<ul>
<li><a href=#home>Home</a></li>
<li><a href=#about>About</a></li>
<li><a href=#portfolio>Progetti</a></li>
<li><a href=#contact>Contatti</a></li>
</ul>
</nav>
</header>
<section class=hero id=home>
<div class=hero-slider>
<div class="slide active" data-bg=/images/char-jardin-1.jpg>
<div class=slide-overlay></div>
</div>
<div class=slide data-bg=/images/giardino-giapponese-8.jpg>
<div class=slide-overlay></div>
</div>
<div class=slide data-bg=/images/locale-commerciale-1.jpg>
<div class=slide-overlay></div>
</div>
<div class=slide data-bg=/images/giardino-giapponese-5.jpg>
<div class=slide-overlay></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=hero-content>
<h1 id=heroTitle></h1>
<p class=hero-subtitle id=heroSubtitle></p>
<a href=#portfolio class=cta-link id=ctaLink>
Vedi progetti<span class=arrow>⟶</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class=nav-arrows>
<button class="arrow-btn prev" id=prevBtn>‹</button>
<button class="arrow-btn next" id=nextBtn>›</button>
</div>
<div class=slide-indicators>
<span class="indicator active" data-slide=0></span>
<span class=indicator data-slide=1></span>
<span class=indicator data-slide=2></span>
<span class=indicator data-slide=3></span>
</div>
<div class=scroll-indicator>
<div class=mouse>
<div class=wheel></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class=about id=about>
<div class=container>
<div class=about-grid>
<div class=about-image>
<img src=/images/foto-giovanna.jpg loading=lazy>
</div>
<div class=about-text>
<p class=section-label><%= data.about.sectionLabel %></p>
<h2><%= data.about.title %></h2>
<p> Sono Giovanna Emanuela Plomitallo, un architetto e mi occupo di progettazione architettonica e interior design, con particolare attenzione alla funzionalità degli spazi e alla qualità estetica degli ambienti. Progetto spazi interni ed esterni (come terrazzi e giardini di piccole dimensioni), valorizzando ogni metro quadrato attraverso soluzioni su misura e studiando la migliore relazione tra luce, materiali e arredo. Il mio approccio è orientato all’ottimizzazione degli spazi, trasformandoli in ambienti accoglienti, efficienti e armoniosi. Mi dedico anche al restyling di case e spazi esistenti, intervenendo con soluzioni mirate che migliorano la fruibilità senza stravolgere l’esistente, quando non necessario. Seguo il progetto in tutte le sue fasi:</p><ul><li>Progetto preliminare e definitivo</li>
<li>
Progetto esecutivo
</li>
<li>Gestione delle pratiche edilizie e della documentazione tecnica</li>
<li>Redazione di computi metrici e coordinamento con le imprese</li>
</ul> Il mio obiettivo è accompagnare il cliente attraverso un percorso chiaro e guidato, dalla prima idea fino alla realizzazione finale, trasformando ogni spazio in un luogo che rispecchi esigenze e identità di chi lo vive.<p></p>
<a href=#portfolio class=btn-portfolio>MIEI PROGETTI</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class=portfolio id=portfolio>
<div class=container>
<div class=portfolio-header>
<p class=section-label><%= data.project.sectionLabel %></p>
<h2><%= data.project.title %></h2>
</div>
<div class=portfolio-grid id=portfolioGrid>
</div>
<div class=portfolio-load-more id=loadMoreContainer style=display:none>
<button class=btn-load-more id=loadMoreBtn>
<span>Carica altri progetti</span>
<svg width=20 height=20 viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill=none stroke=currentColor stroke-width=2>
<polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
</svg>
</button>
<p class=projects-count id=projectsCount></p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<div class=project-modal id=projectModal>
<div class=project-modal-content>
<button class=modal-close id=modalClose>
<svg width=24 height=24 viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill=none stroke=currentColor stroke-width=2>
<line x1=18 y1=6 x2=6 y2=18></line>
<line x1=6 y1=6 x2=18 y2=18></line>
</svg>
</button>
<button class=modal-expand id=modalExpand>
<svg width=24 height=24 viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill=none stroke=currentColor stroke-width=2>
<path d="M8 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v3m18 0V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3m0 18h3a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-3M3 16v3a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h3"></path>
</svg>
</button>
<div class=project-modal-inner>
<div class=project-gallery>
<div class=gallery-main>
<img id=mainImage src="" alt="">
</div>
<div class=gallery-nav>
<button class="gallery-btn gallery-prev" id=galleryPrev>‹</button>
<button class="gallery-btn gallery-next" id=galleryNext>›</button>
</div>
<div class=gallery-counter>
<span id=currentImageIndex>1</span> / <span id=totalImages>4</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class=project-info>
<div class=project-info-scroll>
<h2 id=projectTitle>Titolo immagine.</h2>
<p id=projectDescription class=project-description>Descrivi l'immagine qui.</p>
<div class=project-details>
<div class=detail-item>
<span class=detail-label>LOCALITA'</span>
<span class=detail-value id=projectLocation>—</span>
</div>
<div class=detail-item>
<span class=detail-label>DATA</span>
<span class=detail-value id=projectYear>—</span>
</div>
<div class=detail-item>
<span class=detail-label>TIPOLOGIA</span>
<span class=detail-value id=projectType>—</span>
</div>
<div class=detail-item>
<span class=detail-label>COLLABORAZIONE</span>
<span class=detail-value id=projectCollab>—</span>
</div>
<div class=detail-item>
<span class=detail-label>ESITO</span>
<span class=detail-value id=projectStatus>—</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<section class=contact id=contact>
<div class=container>
<div class=contact-wrapper>
<input type=hidden id=emailTo name=emailTo value="<%= data.contacts.email %>">
<div class=contact-form-container>
<div class=contact-header>
<p class=section-label><%= data.contact_section.sectionLabel %></p>
<h2><%= data.contact_section.title %></h2>
<p class=contact-description><%= data.contact_section.description %></p>
</div>
<form class=contact-form id=contactForm>
<div class=form-group>
<input id=fullName name=fullName placeholder="Nome completo*" required>
</div>
<div class=form-group>
<input type=email id=email name=email placeholder=Email* required>
</div>
<div class=form-group>
<textarea id=message name=message rows=5 placeholder=Messaggio* required></textarea>
</div>
<div class="form-group checkbox-group">
<input type=checkbox id=privacy name=privacy required>
<label for=privacy>Verrà richiesta l'apertura dell'applicazione email predefinita. Cliccando Invia accetta l'apertura.</label>
</div>
<button type=submit class=btn-submit>INVIA</button>
</form>
</div>
<div class=contact-info-container>
<div class=contact-info-box>
<div class=contact-info-item>
<div class=contact-icon>
<svg width=24 height=24 viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill=none stroke=currentColor stroke-width=2>
<path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
<circle cx=12 cy=10 r=3></circle>
</svg>
</div>
<div class=contact-info-text>
<h3>Indirizzo:</h3>
<p id=address_info><%= data.contacts.address %></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class=contact-info-item>
<div class=contact-icon>
<svg width=24 height=24 viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill=none stroke=currentColor stroke-width=2>
<path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
<polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
</svg>
</div>
<div class=contact-info-text>
<h3>EMAIL:</h3>
<p id=email_info><a href="mailto:<%= data.contacts.email %>?subject=From:Portfolio-architettogiovannaplomitallo.it&body=Ciao, ti contatto per..."><%= data.contacts.email %></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class=contact-info-item>
<div class=contact-icon>
<svg width=20 height=20 viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill=none stroke=currentColor stroke-width=2 stroke-linecap=round stroke-linejoin=round>
<path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path>
<rect x=2 y=9 width=4 height=12></rect>
<circle cx=4 cy=4 r=2></circle>
</svg>
</div>
<div class=contact-info-text>
<h3>LINKEDIN:</h3>
<a href="<%= data.contacts.linkedin %> " aria-label=LinkedIn>Giovanna Emanuela Plomitallo</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<footer>
<div class=container>
<div class=footer-content>
<div class=footer-logo>
<h3>GIOVANNA EMANUELA PLOMITALLO</h3>
<p>Architetto</p>
</div>
<div class=footer-links>
<a href=#home>Home</a>
<a href=#about>About</a>
<a href=#portfolio>Portfolio</a>
<a href=#contact>Contatti</a>
</div>
<div class=footer-social>
<a href=https://instagram.com target=_blank rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label=Instagram>
<svg width=20 height=20 viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill=none stroke=currentColor stroke-width=2 stroke-linecap=round stroke-linejoin=round>
<rect x=2 y=2 width=20 height=20 rx=5 ry=5></rect>
<path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path>
<line x1=17.5 y1=6.5 x2=17.51 y2=6.5></line>
</svg>
</a>
<a href=https://linkedin.com target=_blank rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label=LinkedIn>
<svg width=20 height=20 viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill=none stroke=currentColor stroke-width=2 stroke-linecap=round stroke-linejoin=round>
<path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path>
<rect x=2 y=9 width=4 height=12></rect>
<circle cx=4 cy=4 r=2></circle>
</svg>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class=footer-bottom>
<p>&copy; 2025 <%= data.siteTitle %>. All rights reserved.</p>
</div>
</div>
</footer>
<script src=/js/main.js></script>
</body>
</html>